vfio/type1: implement interfaces to update vaddr

Implement VFIO_DMA_UNMAP_FLAG_VADDR, VFIO_DMA_MAP_FLAG_VADDR, and
VFIO_UPDATE_VADDR.  This is a partial implementation.  Blocking is
added in a subsequent patch.

